query.pigql: q = load "ServiceAppointmentDemo"; q = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('EarliestStartTime_Year','EarliestStartTime_Month','EarliestStartTime_Day')")}}; q = filter q by {{column(AssignedResource_Ser_1.result, ["AssignedResource_ServiceResourceId"]).asEquality("AssignedResource_ServiceResourceId")}}; q = filter q by {{column(AvgActualDurationByWorkType.selection, ["ParentRecordId_WorkTypeId_Name"]).asEquality("ParentRecordId_WorkTypeId_Name")}}; q = filter q by 'StatusCategory' == "Completed"; q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate count()/{{column(Time_Selection.selection, ["NumberOfDays"]).asObject()}} as avg_jobs_completed_by_day;

GrainTable.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceAppointmentDemo.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('EarliestStartTime_Year','EarliestStartTime_Month','EarliestStartTime_Day')")}}; q = filter q by {{column(AssignedResource_Ser_1.result, ["AssignedResource_ServiceResourceId"]).asEquality("AssignedResource_ServiceResourceId")}}; q = foreach q generate 'AppointmentNumber' as 'AppointmentNumber',  first('ParentRecordId_WorkOrderNumber') as 'ParentRecordId_WorkOrderNumber', first('ParentRecordId_AccountId_Name') as 'ParentRecordId_AccountId_Name', first('StatusCategory') as 'StatusCategory'; q = order q by 'AppointmentNumber' asc;q = limit q 100;

query.pigql: q = load "ServiceAppointmentDemo"; q = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('EarliestStartTime_Year','EarliestStartTime_Month','EarliestStartTime_Day')")}}; q = filter q by {{column(AssignedResource_Ser_1.result, ["AssignedResource_ServiceResourceId"]).asEquality("AssignedResource_ServiceResourceId")}}; q = filter q by {{column(AvgActualDurationByWorkType.selection, ["ParentRecordId_WorkTypeId_Name"]).asEquality("ParentRecordId_WorkTypeId_Name")}}; i = filter q by 'StatusCategory' == "CannotComplete"; g = group q by all left, i by all; g = foreach g generate (1-(count(i)/count(q)))*100 as sum_first_time_fix;
